Female Youth ages 6-17 join us for our free flag football camp August 5th!
Right after the youth camp, any female athletes 18 years of age or older who think they have what it takes to be apart of our Championship Culture here in Chicago please attend our open tryouts. The Youth Camp and Tryout will be August 5th at Columbus Park outdoor turf (baseball) field. 

Columbus Park 
Turf Baseball Field
500 S. Central Ave
Chicago, Il 60644

Youth Camp: 12:45p-2:15p

Tryout Registration: 12:30p
Open Team Tryouts: 2:15p-4:00p 
***Highly recommend athletes to bring cleats/turf shoes, gloves,  and own liquid hydration.

Our youth flag camp was great a couple of weeks ago despite the weather. The ladies and campers were amazing. We’re definitely looking forward to hosting another soon!
Tamika Robinson is looking forward to competing for the title of XLeague’s #1 ranked WR in 2024!

Big Bee and Kelsey aka Fric & Frac have anchored and solidified our offensive line. These workout partners have great chemistry and durability. Neither missed a snap during our Championship season. Great reasons to why they’re the #1 & #2 ranked offensive line(WOMEN) going into the 2024 season.

The Chicago Blitz have resumed offseason team workouts in preparation for the much anticipated 2nd season of the XLeague. We intend on capturing our 2nd title in a extremely talent stacked league. The work starts now!
